title: Trudeau orders 'take down' of unidentified object in Canadian airspace

title: Cyclone feared to be 'the most serious storm to hit New Zealand this century' closes in
description: A tropical cyclone feared to be the most serious storm to impact New Zealand this century is closing in - days after parts of the country were hit by deadly flooding.

title: Family of five trapped for 129 hours pulled from earthquake rubble

title: Earthquake death toll expected to more than double, says UN aid chief

title: Last prime minister of East Germany dies

title: Toronto mayor resigns after cheating on wife of more than 40 years

title: 'Nightmare scenario' facing Syria as nearly five and a half million people may be left homeless
description: Aid workers have said Syria is facing a "nightmare scenario" as nearly five and a half million people may be left homeless following Monday's devastating earthquake.
